OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLocals step in to help     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftourists after Rhodes fires
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Welsh family who were taken in by    
OL,6, Greek locals when their holiday hotel  
OL,7, was evacuated in the Rhodes wildfires  
OL,8, said it had "restored their faith in   
OL,9, human kindness".                       
OL,11,FCaryn Savazzi travelled to the island  
OL,12,Fwith her husband and sons on Saturday, 
OL,13,Funaware that their hotel had already   
OL,14,Fbeen evacuated amid the blaze.         
OL,16,FThey were taken to a local school,     
OL,17,Fwhere they were offered a place to stay
OL,18,Fin a local family's home.              
OL,20,FBut other Britons remain without a bed.
